==English==

===Etymology===
French ''[[académicien]]''. See [[Academy]].

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A member of an [[academy]], or society for [[promoting]] science, art, or literature, as of the [[French Academy]], or the Royal Academy of Arts.
# {{rare}} A [[collegian]] - [[Chesterfield]]
